@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

title Diagrama de Componente - Minimală

[Mobile App] as mobile
[RabbitMQ] as mq
[Backend API] as api
[Worker Service] as worker
database "SQL Server" as db
[Web Dashboard] as web

mobile --> mq : Telemetry
mobile --> api : Auth
mq --> worker : Messages
worker --> db : Store Data
api --> db : CRUD
web --> api : Requests

note right of mobile
  Colectare OBD-II + GPS
end note

note right of worker
  Procesare asincronă
end note

note right of web
  Vizualizare + Admin
end note

@enduml
